CatDescriptText: Cutline of image or related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 26,1957, reads: "CHURCH TARGET - Spokesman for Ebenezer Baptist Church say the are opposed to a liquor license being issued to Lou Jules' 88 Bar, at 2037 Centre Ave., because the establishment is within 300 feet of Ebenezer Baptist Property."
TitMainTitle: Lou and Jules 88 Bar, 2037 Centre Avenue, in between office of C.G. Nickens M.D., and Hirsch 2 Hour Cleaners, Hill District
